            "effect": "The goblin rabble engage in as coordinated an attack as they can with their dogslicers, attacking each enemy in a 5-foot emanation (DC 18 basic Reflex save). The damage depends on the number of actions. A creature who critically fails their save is also knocked prone.   \n [#] 1d6 slashing damage   \n [##] 2d6+4 slashing damage   \n [###] 2d6+7 slashing damage",
